                                            Customers by City

                                 BUSINESS QUESTION :
"Which cities have more than 100 customers? Show me the city name and customer count, sorted from highest to lowest

                              QUERIES
SELECT
	City,
	COUNT(*) Customercount
FROM telecom_customer
GROUP BY City
HAVING COUNT(*) > 100
ORDER BY COUNT(*)DESC


                              KEY FINDINGS
5 Cities have higher customers
